data.text:
Alexander Eling is an actor, known for Shadowhunters (2016). He portrays Javier Almanzar on Netflix's Another Life.

Biography[]

Alex is from Toronto, Canada. He is an actor and a musician. He can sing and he can also play the drums. He attended Wexford Collegiate School for the Arts. Most of his experience involves theater, he has been involved in many of his school's plays.
